    "description": "EaseMyTrip Consulting Pvt Ltd invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Hotel Manager at our Bhubaneswar location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout EaseMyTrip Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nEaseMyTrip Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Flexible working hours\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhubaneswar, Odisha, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with EaseMyTrip Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
